[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      6[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Focus Areas:** Clinical accuracy, calibration methodology, self-fulfilling prophecy handling, PHI in real-time inference, fairness/subgroup performance, ICU data pipeline reliability
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      7[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
